In dotfile directory follow this step:
    git submodule init
    git submodule add <git_repository_of_submodule> <path_to_save_submodule>
    git add .gitmodules <path_to_save_submodule>
    git commit

    e.g.

    git submodule init
    git submodule add https://github.com/vim-airline/vim-airline.git vim/pack/shapeshed/start/vim-airline
    git add .gitmodules vim/pack/shapeshed/start/vim-airline
    git commit

To upgrade de submodules:
    git submodule update --remote --merge
    git commit
